text: Emma Jeffcoat is an Australian triathlete. ==Career== Emma Jeffcoat starts in the German Bundesliga for the club Komet Team TV Lemgo. [1] In March 2016 she became a champion of the U23-Oceania triathlon and second-class Oceania champion in the elite class.Emma Jeffcoat An Athlete Making Moves (11 August 2014) ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Australian female triathletes Category:Living people
